;
;---------------------------------------------------
;
; coding
;
;---------------------------------------------------
;
;
C00,Comfort System (J393) Coding
C01,+00001 = Selective Locking inactive
C02,+00002 = 4-Doors (only with Sliding Door Rear Left AND Right)
C03,+00004 = Sliding Door Rear Left
C04,+00008 = Sliding Door Rear Right
C05,+00016 = Central Locking installed (from MY 2008)
C06,+00016 = Central Locking without Power Windows installed (through MY 2007)
C07,+00064 = Central Locking with Power Windows installed (through MY 2007)
C08,+01024 = Power Windows without Central Locking installed (through MY 2007)
C09, 
C10,Note: The Coding is the Sum of the individual Options. As of MY 2008 the Door
C11,Control Modules are now connected via LIN which results in different codings.
;
